text.section:
Except as provided in subsection (d) of this section, within 30 days of receipt of the duplicate certificate, the supervisor shall have two assessors:
Independently of each other, inspect and assess the actual fair market value of the vacant land and any improvements on it;
Endorse the duplicate certificate with their joint determination of the assessed value of the vacant land and improvements;
Prepare a statement of the reasons for the valuation;
Sign and verify the endorsed duplicate certificate and the statement; and
Return the endorsed duplicate certificate and the statement to the Commissioner.
